# Place a .env file in each workspace folder to inject secrets.
# These become workspace-level secrets (encrypted, never exposed to browser).
#
# Model authentication uses the platform token flow by default. Add an optional
# BYOK value only when the selected runtime/model explicitly declares it.
#
# Each workspace folder can have its own .env with different keys.
# A .env at the org root is shared across all workspaces (workspace overrides
# win), so keep role-specific integration credentials in that role's folder.
